dreisoft.tresos.generator.ng.api.cds.ctypes

Interface IConditionalMembers


  • public interface IConditionalMembers
    Implement this interface in your Struct class to be able to skip members that should not be generated.

    Since:
    2008.b

    • Method Detail

      • exists

        boolean exists(java.lang.String memberName)
        Determines if the member with the given name exists and should be generated. This method gets invoked by the cds engine.
        Parameters:
        memberName - The name of the member field.
        Returns:
        true if the member should be generated, false otherwise.
        Since:
        2008.b
